metadata.name: Cyber Island
metadata.description: In a corner of Cyber Island, there was a young hacker named Amy. Every day, she traveled through the virtual world in search of new challenges. One day, Amy stumbled upon a mysterious program, but her attempts to access it were met with powerful resistance. She decided to enlist the help of some like-minded friends to conquer this seemingly impenetrable program. After a long and intense battle, they finally succeeded in unlocking the secrets of the program, gaining immense wealth and reputation in the process. From then on, Amy and her small group of companions became legendary figures on Cyber Island.
